StackBlitz link: https://stackblitz.com/edit/stackblitz-starters-57cqqc?file=src%2Fapp%2Fviewport-error.component.html
Steps to reproduce:
1. open the mat-menu
2. the viewport is half empty
3. resize the window
4. viewport filled properly

